overview.en: TOKOK is a global and professional Cryptocurrency Exchange Platform, affiliated to Kindly Keep Network Technology Limited。It provides Crypto-currencies trading services. Through the professional management team, platform supported by advanced technology, strict capital management system and considerate services, we're dedicated to a world-class Cryptocurrency exchange platform.TOK is a token issued by TOKOK. Users holding TOK enjoy  discounts when using TOK to pay for transaction fees and get dividends with development of the platform.
overview.zh: TOKOK是隶属于英属维京公司Kindly Keep Network Technology Limited旗下面向全球服务的专业加密资产交易平台。TOKOK以来自世界各地的专业的管理团队、强大技术支撑的交易系统、安全严格的资金管理、贴心的服务，为用户提供加密资产交易服务，打造世界级的加密资产交易平台。TOK是TOKOK交易平台的代币；持有TOK代币可以享受TOKOK平台手续费的折扣优惠、平台利润的分红等。
